thread.title: Bridget Goulding
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Bridget Goulding

author: Bridget Goulding
title: Bridget Goulding
text: Staff were very friendly and helpful - especially bloke who dropped us back to airport after our trip away. Car was ready for us to pick up when we got to depot at start of trip. I had booked on line so the paperwork only required signing and licences getting copied - basically trouble free.
